Title: KitchenAid - Shop the Icon
Author: wavelet-director

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

A KitchenAid stand mixer in glossy empire-red sits on a cream marble counter. A cloud of flour blooms upward as dough lands in the bowl. Soft window light from the left.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Two hands gently lower the tilt-head into place over the bowl. The iconic curved housing locks down with a precise mechanical motion.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Macro: the spiral dough hook rotates slowly. Pale dough catches the hook, folds over itself, and starts to climb the spindle.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Macro: the wire whip turns inside a chilled metal bowl. Cream lifts into glossy stiff peaks, ribbons sliding off the whip.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

A linen-wrapped hand pulls a deep-crusted sourdough loaf from a hot oven. Steam catches the light.

CUT TO:

INT. WARM KITCHEN - MORNING

Wide shot. The finished loaf rests on a wooden board, knife beside it. The empire-red stand mixer sits softly out of focus in the background.

CUT TO:

INT. STUDIO - DAY

The KitchenAid wordmark holds against an empire-red field. A small "A WHIRLPOOL BRAND" line sits beneath it. A cream button reads "SHOP THE ICON".

FADE OUT.
